2026-04-21T20:55:09.3214203Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-04-21T20:55:09.3214967Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-04-21T20:55:09.3215660Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-04-21T20:55:09.3216515Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-04-21T20:55:09.3217391Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-04-21T20:55:09.3218253Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-04-21T20:55:09.3219091Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-04-21T20:55:09.3219947Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-04-21T20:55:09.3220791Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-04-21T20:55:09.3221575Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-04-21T20:55:09.3222197Z 33    -->
