2026-04-21T20:55:09.4214850Z 12    <!--
2026-04-21T20:55:09.4215063Z 13        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-04-21T20:55:09.4215260Z 14        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
